  "title": "Storekeeper",
  "description": "<p><strong>Shangri-La Rasa Sentosa, Singapore</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are looking for a <strong>Storekeeper (F&amp;B)</strong> to join our team!</p>\n<p>As a <strong>Storekeeper (F&amp;B)</strong>, we rely on you to:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure that goods recieved are in good condition and of the required quantity and quality ordered</li>\n  <li>Raise purchasing requisition to replenish the inventory of store items</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper recording of the inventory</li>\n  <li>Preparation of daily and monthly report, including invenrtory report after stocktaking</li>\n  <li>Ensuring hygiene and sanitation standards are well-maintained</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>We are looking for someone who:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Must be detailed-orientated and meticulous in record keeping</li>\n  <li>Relevant experiences in Food &amp; Beverage/Culinary store management</li>\n  <li>Posses relevant food hygiene certification</li>\n  <li>Posses driving license is an added advantage</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>We Offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5-day work week</li>\n  <li>Learning and Development opportunities for career development</li>\n  <li>Medical and insurance coverage</li>\n  <li>Special employee discount within Shangri-La Group</li>\n  <li>Duty Meals and shuttle bus provided</li>\n</ul>",
